## Source IP Identification

The student's public IP was identified using:
```bash
curl ifconfig.me
# Result: 102.88.55.250
```

This was applied as `102.88.55.250/32` in both NSG inbound rules.

> **Note:** This IP is dynamically assigned by the ISP and may change. If connection is lost after a network change, update the NSG source IP to the new public IP address.

